response.original_title: Danielle Dax - Bad Miss M Live
response.overview: Recorded at the Camden Palace Theatre, London, on the 30th of December 1985, this DVD is the showcase for the artist, musician, actress. Completely taken over by her onstage person, Danielle seamlessly combines theatre and music to anstonishing and beautiful effect as she performs an intense and moving set.
response.title: Danielle Dax - Bad Miss M Live
